---
title: Korma-Style Chicken Breast Curry with Rice and Garlic Flatbreads
description: Aromatics and spices come together perfectly in this velvety, cashew-based chicken curry. Add a fluffy bed of rice and garlicky flatbreads and your stomach is going to be smiling!

